TypeCompatibility
public static record TypeCompatibility.TypeCompatibilityReport(boolean isCompatible, @Nullable com.sun.tools.javac.code.Type lhs, @Nullable com.sun.tools.javac.code.Type rhs, @Nullable String extraReason) extends Record
The result of a TypeCompatibility.compatibilityOfTypes(Type, Type, VisitorState) call.

If isCompatible is true, the other fields are null.
